# 🧠 Mental Model

For each industry, answer 3 things:

1. **Who is the buyer?** (budget owner)
2. **What is the core use case?** (value driver)
3. **What pricing aligns with value?** (monetization)

---

# 🇮🇳 Industry-wise Breakdown (India-focused)

---

## 1. IT Services / SaaS (Infosys, TCS, startups)

### 👤 Buyer

* CTO / VP Engineering
* Head of Platform / Dev Productivity

### 💡 Use cases

* Code generation (Copilot-style)
* Internal copilots
* Dev productivity tools

### 💰 Best pricing models

**→ Token-based (primary)**
**→ Seat + credits (secondary)**

### Why?

* Usage is unpredictable (dev workflows vary)
* Cost tied to compute

👉 Example:

* API products → token pricing
* Dev tools → seat + usage hybrid

---

## 2. BFSI (Banks, Fintech, Insurance)

### 👤 Buyer

* Chief Digital Officer
* Head of Operations / Risk

### 💡 Use cases

* Customer support automation
* Document processing (KYC, claims)
* Risk analysis

### 💰 Best pricing models

**→ Outcome-based (ideal)**
**→ Per-document / per-case (practical)**

### Why?

* Value = cost saved per case / fraud prevented
* High willingness to pay for accuracy

👉 Example:

* ₹ per loan processed
* ₹ per claim resolved

---

## 3. E-commerce / Retail (Flipkart, Reliance, D2C brands)

### 👤 Buyer

* Head of Growth
* Head of Marketing / CX

### 💡 Use cases

* Product descriptions
* Chatbots
* Personalization

### 💰 Best pricing models

**→ Output-based (best)**
**→ API/request-based (infra layer)**

### Why?

* Value = content generated / conversions improved
* Easy to map output → revenue

👉 Example:

* ₹ per product description
* ₹ per chatbot conversation

---

## 4. Healthcare (Hospitals, Healthtech)

### 👤 Buyer

* Chief Medical Officer
* Operations Head
* Compliance teams

### 💡 Use cases

* Clinical documentation
* Patient triage
* Medical coding

### 💰 Best pricing models

**→ Per-report / per-patient (output-based)**
**→ Outcome-based (advanced)**

### Why?

* Strong compliance + accuracy needs
* Billing tied to workflows

👉 Example:

* ₹ per discharge summary
* ₹ per diagnosis assist

---

## 5. Manufacturing / Supply Chain (TVS, Tata, etc.)

### 👤 Buyer

* Head of Operations
* Supply chain leadership

### 💡 Use cases

* Demand planning
* SOP copilots
* Maintenance logs / reports

### 💰 Best pricing models

**→ Subscription + usage hybrid**
**→ Outcome-based (long-term)**

### Why?

* Continuous usage + workflow integration
* ROI tied to efficiency (not tokens)

👉 Example:

* Monthly fee + usage
* ₹ per % improvement in forecast accuracy

---

## 6. EdTech / Education

### 👤 Buyer

* Founder / Product Head
* Institutional buyers (schools, colleges)

### 💡 Use cases

* AI tutors
* Content generation
* Grading

### 💰 Best pricing models

**→ Seat-based (students/teachers)**
**→ Usage caps (fair usage)**

### Why?

* Easy procurement
* Predictable budgets

👉 Example:

* ₹ per student per month

---

## 7. HRTech / Recruiting (your domain 👀)

### 👤 Buyer

* Head of Talent / CHRO
* Recruiting ops leaders

### 💡 Use cases

* Resume screening
* JD generation
* Candidate outreach

### 💰 Best pricing models

**→ Per-job / per-hire (outcome-based)**
**→ Seat + credits (hybrid)**

### Why?

* Value = hiring efficiency / time saved
* Strong alignment with business KPI

👉 Example:

* ₹ per job processed
* ₹ per qualified candidate

---

## 8. Marketing Agencies / LLM SEO (emerging in India)

### 👤 Buyer

* CMO
* Growth / digital teams

### 💡 Use cases

* LLM visibility (AI search)
* Content optimization for AI answers

(huge emerging space in India due to shift from SEO → AI answers ([FTA Global][2]))

### 💰 Best pricing models

**→ Subscription + performance bonus**
**→ Outcome-based (traffic / leads)**

---

## 9. Customer Support / BPO (massive in India)

### 👤 Buyer

* Head of Support
* COO

### 💡 Use cases

* AI agents
* Ticket resolution
* Voice/chat automation

### 💰 Best pricing models

**→ Per-ticket / per-resolution (best)**
**→ Per-minute (voice AI)**

### Why?

* Direct cost replacement (agents → AI)

👉 Example:

* ₹ per ticket resolved
* ₹ per call handled

---

# 🔥 Synthesis: Mapping Models to Industries

| Industry      | Buyer         | Best Pricing Model     |
| ------------- | ------------- | ---------------------- |
| IT / SaaS     | CTO           | Token / Seat + credits |
| BFSI          | Ops / Risk    | Outcome / per-case     |
| E-commerce    | Growth        | Output-based           |
| Healthcare    | Ops / Medical | Per-report / outcome   |
| Manufacturing | Ops           | Hybrid / outcome       |
| EdTech        | Product       | Seat-based             |
| HRTech        | Talent        | Per-hire / hybrid      |
| Marketing     | CMO           | Subscription + outcome |
| BPO           | Support head  | Per-ticket             |

